{"tid":2447351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約街頭發現「中国殺人」口罩","createTime":"2021-03-15T06:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T12:36:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":77,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"bf7f2db2df595bf373d999da2462f2eaa9c7274e","tid":2447351,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.worldjournal.com/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/wj/paper/2021/03/15/11878709.jpeg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;q=75&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.worldjournal.com%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fwj%2Fpaper%2F2021%2F03%2F15%2F11878709.jpeg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26q%3D75%26nt%3D1&h=18887d02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n布碌崙(布魯克林)華裔聚集的戴克高地街頭，14日突然出現一個寫有「中國殺人」(China Kills)的口罩，被民眾發現後拍照發布網路，引起眾多網友譴責，紛紛表示該類針對華裔的仇恨言論與行為已入侵社區各個角落，造成巨大傷害，無能再容忍。<br />\n<br />\n居住在戴克高地的華女陳賀喆(Hazel Chen，音譯)14日上午10時40分左右，步行前往超市買菜期間，在13大道交66街街口發現地上丟棄的一個口罩，上面用黑色的筆寫著「中國殺人」(China Kills)。<br />\n<br />\n陳女士說，看到後一股恐懼感瞬間湧上頭，還擔心是有感染新冠病毒患者故意丟棄在此的，不敢用手將口罩拿起來，只是拿出手機拍了照；陳女士買完菜原路返回時本來打算想找個樹枝，將口罩挑起來丟去垃圾桶，但是發現該口罩已經不見。<br />\n<br />\n陳女士說，自己來美四年多，這是一次親眼目睹針對華裔的仇恨言論和行為，「我原本以為那些仇恨只發生在電視新聞裡，沒想到原來離我們這麼近」；最近不斷發生的仇恨犯罪，過去已經讓陳女士天黑就不敢再出門丟垃圾，經歷此事，她更是心驚膽顫。<br />\n<br />\n陳女士之後將照片發給紐約親子互助會會長黃妮可，黄妮可將照片發布網路，引起民眾討論與譴責；不少民眾表示，現在針對華裔的仇恨言論與行為已經到了無法再容忍的地步。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121382/5318561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2Fwj%2Fstory%2F121382%2F5318561&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=639bb092\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121382/5318561</a>"},{"pid":"1839a7c00ea1d89dea7e23099ba13798151281d4","tid":2447351,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:56:17.000Z","msg":"馬英狗看手錶"},{"pid":"68f553e29e01ddc2705962a94e33f5be6685b351","tid":2447351,"uid":125357,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:56:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">China Kills<br />\n支那殺人</span>"},{"pid":"db3912a9c717013d9e990be33789e477c5c2f420","tid":2447351,"uid":13503,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:57:47.000Z","msg":"我覺得係中共又想大造新聞又玩全國抗美嘅劇本"},{"pid":"f57f38baa915cdbf9a1a1be332bc86a399294c64","tid":2447351,"uid":155723,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:58:15.000Z","msg":"facts<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"741184bc0cccdc0c33f38558059323054072c3e8","tid":2447351,"uid":36567,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"針對華裔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來China係解華裔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6946d3d3e26878a979b701cf6381dc4b010e6166","tid":2447351,"uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FKLTUnu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFKLTUnu.jpg&h=64a3fa8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0ed08383e720035ae10e3a6aa1976d1768e096d","tid":2447351,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"741184bc0cccdc0c33f38558059323054072c3e8","tid":2447351,"uid":36567,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"針對華裔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來China係解華裔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:58:59.000Z","msg":"係蝗裔"},{"pid":"c74fcdbbc390e524cd7a1e8dad5f757e3139bc36","tid":2447351,"uid":256143,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"求其寫隻字落口罩再放地下影相就成功炒起話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6251e9f946c4234ce4e155f2dbb3a175ba198203","tid":2447351,"uid":214679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n陳女士說，自己來美四年多，這是一次親眼目睹針對華裔的仇恨言論和行為，「我原本以為那些仇恨只發生在電視新聞裡，沒想到原來離我們這麼近</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼續玩微信，生活喺華人圈子入面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd082a2ff975907cdc4fa7295630454fee18b4f","tid":2447351,"uid":327462,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:01:51.000Z","msg":"咪又係無國家出嚟追討武肺責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f83c5c127824cce0daab3c528ba6ad4275f05b9","tid":2447351,"uid":33263,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:03:31.000Z","msg":"幾時排華<br />\n同再追責賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ed6d0ee2698bcb13f9a0b4a8154bc3f74302f7","tid":2447351,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"香港人要做既唔係左膠反歧視<br />\n係要區分支那人出去<br />\n唔好比佢地再扮香港人<br />\n同時一齊排支"},{"pid":"8247bab35da6aa0364ac87edfdcfcd0a9f0f6efe","tid":2447351,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"741184bc0cccdc0c33f38558059323054072c3e8","tid":2447351,"uid":36567,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"針對華裔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來China係解華裔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"CHINESE就係解華裔<br />\n係你班港豬咁鐘意叫自己華裔做支那豬"},{"pid":"a98f29afae993eaefbd654c841537537a328e313","tid":2447351,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:10:11.000Z","msg":"又可以賴侵"},{"pid":"17224d873d3c6f767162ccccc5dc42e6115ec2bb","tid":2447351,"uid":285415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8247bab35da6aa0364ac87edfdcfcd0a9f0f6efe","tid":2447351,"uid":253016,